OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772917925
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing suspected violent assault
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder, following the death of a
OL,8,Fman near Redcar.
OL,10,FJust after 8pm on Friday evening (6
OL,11,FMarch), police were called by the
OL,12,Fambulance service, who were treating a
OL,13,Fman with serious injuries in an
OL,14,Falleyway between Dale Street and
OL,15,FArthur Terrace in New Marske.
OL,17,FOfficers believe he had been the
OL,18,Fvictim of a violent assault, and he
OL,19,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene just
OL,20,Fover an hour later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772917925
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing suspected violent assault
OL,6,FPolice have said extensive enquiries
OL,7,Finto the circumstances surrounding the
OL,8,Fman's death are underway, and formal
OL,9,Fidentification will take place in due
OL,10,Fcourse.
OL,12,FA 37-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Cleveland Police said:
OL,16,F"While we understand this incident
OL,17,Fwill have caused concern in the local
OL,18,Fcommunity, at this stage we believe it
OL,19,Fto be an isolated and targeted event.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772917925
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing suspected violent assault
OL,6,F"Police will remain in the area
OL,7,Fprogressing enquiries as well as
OL,8,Fproviding a reassuring presence to
OL,9,Fresidents.
OL,11,F"Please speak to our officers if you
OL,12,Fhave any concerns.
OL,14,F"As enquiries are in their very early
OL,15,Fstages, we would urge people not to
OL,16,Fspeculate or comment online."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
